      "text": "（トリエルが、人気アニメを原作とする舞台の）\n（主演に決まった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（TRINITYAiLE has been chosen for the lead role in a stage play）\n（based on a popular anime.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（舞台はいつものステージと勝手が違うし、大変だろう）\n（俺も頑張ってサポートしていかないと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（A stage play is different from their usual performances‚ so it'll be tough.）\n（I should do my best to support them too.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 12.1761223634
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん、ふふーん……\nあ！　{user}さん、お疲れ様です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm~‚ hmm hmm~…\nAh! {user}-san‚ good work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 157.21096990000126,
          "startTime": 12.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 18.5378453732
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "……って、あれ、どうしたんですか？\nなんだか、ちょっと疲れた顔してるみたいですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Um‚ hello? What's wrong?\nSomehow‚ you look a bit tired.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうか？　最近、仕事が立て込んでるせいで\nそう見えるのかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do I? Maybe it's because work has been piling up lately‚\nso I might look that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 31.8422226746
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それよりすみれこそ、舞台の準備と並行して各局の番組\nにもひっぱりだこで疲れが溜まってるんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More than that‚ Sumire‚ you're preparing for the stage while also\nbeing in demand for TV shows. Aren't you getting tired?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.5333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 39.9322227001
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……スケジュールが詰まってますし\n移動中も台本読み込んでて、大変は大変ですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… my schedule is packed‚\nand I even read scripts while traveling‚ so it is tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_10_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "でも子役でドラマに出てた頃も、クランクインした後は\n稽古と撮影を繰り返すのが普通でしたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when I was a child actor in dramas‚ once filming began‚\nit was normal to just keep repeating rehearsals and shooting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.0666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
